column2: Tarmac - Run 1/4 Crew Runweight Merino Wool Sock

Our  StrongStrut® arch support provides arch support while eliminating blister causing slippage and our  FreeVent® airflow design works to keep the your foot dry in the area it needs it most. Wool is naturally moisture-wicking and odor-resistant. USA-Made, lifetime warranty.

column2: Campfire - Hike Crew Lightweight Merino Wool Copy
column3: Our Campfire Merino Wool Sock is the ideal companion for your summer adventures.  Made with 53% merino wool, 41% nylon, and 6% elastane, this 10" crew height offers warmth and protection from both footwear and the elements, and our lightweight cushion profile puts the padding in the areas where your foot needs it most. By removing the cushion in the mid-foot area, we create a sock that is more efficient in regulating heat and moisture for those hot days on the trail. With seamless toes, StrongStrut® arch-support, and  FreeVent® zones that provide enhanced breathability and moisture management, this sock is the ideal daily driver for those who depend on their feet.  Moisture-wicking, odor-resistant, and USA-Made with a lifetime warranty.
